FastPattern.description: 6, IPSecTrafficAudit: VPN; Initiating new phase negotiation

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Allowed requested URL \S+ from the host [\d.]+ as the (?:keyword|URL) matched\.

FastField.defaultValue: Allowed requested URL as the $7 matched

FastPattern.description: 13, WebTrafficAudit: ProtectLink; Allowing blocked or low reputation URL
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \[(\w+)\]\[(\w*)\] Allowing blocked or low reputation URL from client ([\d.]+)\. (.+)
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Allowing blocked or low reputation URL from client [\d.]+\. (.+)

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \[(\w+)\]\[(\w*)\] Blocked requested URL (\S+) from host ([\d.]+) as it matched with the blocked URL (.+)
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Blocked requested URL \S+ from host [\d.]+ as it matched with the blocked URL

FastPattern.description: 15, WebTrafficAudit: ProtectLink; Sending request for URL

FastFormatter.condition: The URL \(.+\) accessed from IP \([\d.]+\) has been identified as ([/\w ]+) site and.*

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[FIREWALL\]\[\w*\] (?:Added|Deleted) firewall rule \w+ for service \w+ with action \w+

FastFormatter.condition: (\w+) firewall rule (\w+) for service (\w+) with action (\w+)
FastFormatter.format: $6 firewall rule "$7" for service "$8" with action "$9"

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] (?:Approved Clients List|Content Filtering|Overflow Control|Policy Enforcement) is (?:Disabled|Enabled)\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[FIREWALL\]\[\w*\] Restarting traffic meter with \d+ mins, \d+ hours, \d+ Day of Month\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[FIREWALL\]\[\w*\] Traffic meter enabled with no limit type\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Categories to signature mappings updated successfully\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] enabling IPS checks between \w+ and \w+ zones\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Latest available IPS signature version: \w+; Present IPS signature version: \w+\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] By default all URLs except the Blocked URLs are allowed

FastPattern.description: 38, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; Detect a white list

FastPattern.description: 39, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; Found at beginning of domain
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Found ".+" at the beginning of the domain\. Trim it\. code=-?\d+
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Open a socket \(\d+\) with familiy=\d+, socktype=\d+, protocol=\d+ successfully\.\. code=-?\d+

FastFormatter.condition: Rating URL: domain=[-\w.]+ \(\d+\), (port=\d+, path=\S+ \(\d+\), ip=[()\w.]+)\. code=-?\d+.*

FastPattern.description: 51, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; Raw result from RS

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Resolving IP address of [-\w:.]+ successully\.\. code=-?\d+

FastPattern.description: 57, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; The key for the cache
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] The key \(length = \d+\) for the cache is

FastFormatter.condition: The key \(length = \d+\) for the cache is '([^']+)'\..*
The key \(length = \d+\) for the cache is '([^']+)

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Trying to connect to [-\w:.]+ without proxy\.\. code=-?\d+

FastFormatter.condition: Trying to connect to ([-\w:.]+) without proxy
FastFormatter.format: Trying to connect to "$8" without proxy

FastPattern.description: 60, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; Trying to get rating
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \[(\w+)\]\[(\w*)\] Trying to get rating data from RS: (.+)\. code=(-?\d+).*
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Trying to get rating data from RS: '[^']+' via type \d+ proxy: '[^']+'\. code=-?\d+

FastField.defaultValue: Trying to get rating data from RS

FastPattern.description: 61, ServiceInfo: ProtectLink; Update cache with result
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Update cache with result from RS\. Key=

FastFormatter.condition: Update cache with result from RS\. Key='([^']+)'\..*
Update cache with result from RS\. Key='([^']+)

FastPattern.description: 73, ServiceInfo: VPN; Using IPsec SA configuration

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Another upgrade process is running now\. Postponing the auto-update check by \d+ hour

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Failed to delete [-\w ]+ entry from crontab

\d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Failed to query the available signatures' information from remote server
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[IPS\]\[\w*\] Failed to trigger the first row in IPSIntegration table

FastPattern.description: 84, ServiceWarning: ProtectLink; Can't open a socket

FastField.defaultValue: Can't open a socket and establish a connection to "$5"

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Can not connect to host [-\w:.]+!\. code=-?\d+

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) \[(\w+)\]\[(\w*)\] Fail to connect to ([-\w:.]+)\. Try to close socket socket (\d+)! Err: (-?\d+)\. code=(-?\d+).*
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Fail to connect to [-\w:.]+\. Try to close socket socket \d+! Err: -?\d+\. code=-?\d+

FastField.defaultValue: Try to close socket socket $6, Error: $7

FastPattern.description: 89, ServiceWarning: ProtectLink; Fail to get data
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Fail to get data from RS!? \(?ErrorCode=-?\d+\)?[!.](?: Try to use the alternative RS\.\.)? code=-?\d+

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Fail to (?:lookup the URL from the remote server|process and normalize the URL)! ErrorCode=-?\d+\. code=-?\d+

FastPattern.description: 94, ServiceWarning: ProtectLink; No result is found
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] No result is found (?:for the request URL|in the Cache|in the local db)\.\. code=-?\d+
\d+ [-\w.]+ \[ProtectLink\]\[\w*\] Recv data timeout at socket \d+!\. code=-?\d+
